# Per-task scratch — ephemeral notes the agent appends while a ticket is in
# `testing/`. Convention: a ticket `NNN-*.md` may have a sibling
# `NNN-*.scratch.md` that is never committed. At conclude time the agent
# either summarises the scratch into the ticket's body or discards it.
# See ADR-0017 trail + pipeline ticket 042 for the convention.
*.scratch.md
